DESCRIPTION:Create your own playful patchwork cat with artist Vasundhara W in this fun\, hands-on workshop inspired by geometric shapes and fabric craft. Using tangram-style forms\, colourful fabric\, and simple stitching techniques\, participants will design amusing cats in a variety of poses.\n\nBy the end of the session\, you’ll have a fun patchwork cat placemat to take home.\n\nThis event is part of the closing weekend celebrations for The Many Lives of the Cat.
DTEND:20260329T110000Z
