DESCRIPTION:Image Credits: Anoushka\nHow well do you know the history of the Deccan?  Test your knowledge of Karnataka’s rich heritage through a sharp\, engaging quiz at MAP\, in collaboration with Ace of Pubs. Journey across historic sites\, architectural landmarks\, and cultural histories that shape the region—one question at a time.
